  "detailed_description": "LUNARiA -Virtualized Moonchild- is a digital novel made by visual novel studio Key.<br>There are no story branches based on choices. The story proceeds as if you were watching an anime or movie, or turning the pages of a novel.<br>Enjoy a touching story with beautiful music and graphics, realistic and colorful performances, brought to life by talented voice actors.<br><br><strong>Game features</strong><br>・With support for full HD resolution of 1920x1080 dots, you can enjoy the moving story in high-definition visuals.<br><br>・The text can be set to English, Japanese, or Simplified Chinese (audio only available in Japanese). This includes in-game text, options, and the digital manual. Language settings can be changed at any time.<br><br>・Touch gestures can also be used if you're playing on a tablet PC or a Steam Deck.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983260/extras/8de8ff073322866274032b2a7926130b.avif?t=1732683383\" width=616 height=374 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983260/extras/f7ec72031a78c61844abae4a47b91298.webp?t=1732683383\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983260/extras/b81f82f465b9f06e8328ed56270c06d4.avif?t=1732683383\" width=616 height=449 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983260/extras/a6a402e8b0e6e159adaf677a340d5cee.webp?t=1732683383\" width=616 height=62 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983260/extras/0568146ca36dc63c895909892f080afa.webp?t=1732683383\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstati